[normal]&#xa0;[bold]7. As a contributory factor to conditions including diabetes, heart failure and coronary heart disease, how can we address obesity?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Obesity is well known to be a fundamental risk factor for a series of conditions, such as diabetes, heart failure and coronary heart disease
[normal]. 
[normal]Its impact on psychological problems, low self esteem and even suicide risk should also not be forgotten. The impact on health budgets, workload and service development is immense.
[normal] 
